    <p data-i18n-en="The self-test loss is agnostic to how V and &Phi; are parameterized. We implement it two ways:"
       data-i18n-zh="自测损失函数不关心 V 和 &Phi; 的参数化方式。我们用两种方式实现：">
      The self-test loss is agnostic to how V and &Phi; are parameterized. We implement it two ways:
