        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
          data-i18n-en="Expand V, &Phi; in known polynomial/exponential basis functions. Solve via linear least squares — exact, fast, but requires prior knowledge of the potential form."
          data-i18n-zh="用已知的多项式/指数基函数展开 V、&Phi;。通过线性最小二乘求解——精确、快速，但需要预先知道势函数形式。">
          Expand V, &Phi; in known polynomial/exponential basis functions. Solve via linear least squares — exact, fast, but requires prior knowledge of the potential form.
