      <!-- NN Self-Test card -->
      <div style="background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.25); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">&#x1F9E0;</span>
          <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #22c55e;"
            data-i18n-en="Self-Test NN"
            data-i18n-zh="自测 NN">Self-Test NN</h3>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
          data-i18n-en="Parameterize V, &Phi; with MLPs. Optimize via gradient descent — flexible, no prior knowledge needed, but requires training."
          data-i18n-zh="用 MLP 参数化 V、&Phi;。通过梯度下降优化——灵活，不需要先验知识，但需要训练。">
          Parameterize V, &Phi; with MLPs. Optimize via gradient descent — flexible, no prior knowledge needed, but requires training.
        </p>
        <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
          <span style="color: #22c55e;">&check;</span>
          <span data-i18n-en="No prior knowledge" data-i18n-zh="无需先验知识">No prior knowledge</span><br/>
          <span style="color: #f59e0b;">&times;</span>
          <span data-i18n-en="Requires training" data-i18n-zh="需要训练">Requires training</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.05); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #22c55e; font-weight: 600;"
        data-i18n-en="&#x2193; Same self-test loss &#x2193;"
        data-i18n-zh="&#x2193; 同一个自测损失 &#x2193;">&#x2193; Same self-test loss &#x2193;</p>
      <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);"
        data-i18n-en="The loss is our contribution, not the parameterization. Both implementations share the same theoretical guarantee."
        data-i18n-zh="损失函数是我们的贡献，不是参数化方式。两种实现共享同一个理论保证。">
