      <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;"
        data-i18n-en="Left: Least squares regression with basis functions. Right: Neural network regression via gradient descent. Both share the same self-test loss."
        data-i18n-zh="左：基函数最小二乘回归。右：神经网络梯度下降回归。两者共享同一个自测损失。">
        Left: Least squares regression with basis functions. Right: Neural network regression via gradient descent. Both share the same self-test loss.
