  <!-- ═══ Section 6: Models ═══ -->
  <section id="models" class="section section-wide">
    <p class="section-label"
      data-i18n-en="Stress Tests"
      data-i18n-zh="压力测试">Stress Tests</p>
    <h2 data-i18n-en="Stress Tests: Four Models"
        data-i18n-zh="压力测试：四种模型">Stress Tests: Four Models</h2>
    <p data-i18n-en="Each model tests a different theoretical boundary. The Reference model (E) is our main benchmark; models A-D each stress-test a specific assumption."
       data-i18n-zh="每个模型测试一个不同的理论边界。参考模型（E）是主要基准；模型A-D各自压力测试一个特定假设。">
      Each model tests a different theoretical boundary. The Reference model (E) is our main benchmark; models A-D each stress-test a specific assumption.
