       data-i18n-zh="更多快照 M &rarr; 统计误差按 1/&radic;M 下降。离散化偏差取决于积分法则：Riemann 和对应 &alpha;=1（O(&Delta;t) 下限），梯形/chordwise 法则对应 &alpha;=2（O((&Delta;t)&sup2;) 下限）。见下方图 2 的对比。">
      More snapshots M &rarr; statistical error drops as 1/&radic;M. The discretization bias depends on the quadrature rule: &alpha;=1 for Riemann sum (O(&Delta;t) floor), &alpha;=2 for trapezoidal/chordwise rule (O((&Delta;t)&sup2;) floor). See Figure 2 below for the comparison.
    </p>

